ingredients_text: Sugar, palm oil, hazelnuts (13%), skimmed milk powder (8.7%), fat-reduced cocoa (7.4%), emulsifier: lecithins (soya), vanillin

Sugar, wheat flour, palm and/or canola oil, cocoa powder (processed with alkali) (4.6%), high fructose corn syrup, leavening (baking soda and/or calcium phosphate), salt, soy lecithin, vanillin (artificial flavor), chocolate
Water, hulled soya beans (8.7%), apple extract, acidity regulator (dipotassium phosphate), calcium (calcium carbonate), sea salt, stabiliser (gellan gum), vitamins (B2, B12, D2)
Carbonated water, sugar, colour (caramel E150d), phosphoric acid, natural flavourings including caffeine
